{"tid":2102251,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"退休藍絲機場揮拳傷「和你飛」示威者　  輕判：判囚3個月緩刑2年","createTime":"2020-07-10T10:35:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T10:51:15.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e9a447e0fe055d065b69e4b1810e4e23abe2d6b3","tid":2102251,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:35:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200708/s00001/1594186659457/退休漢機場揮拳傷人-判囚3個月緩刑2年\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200708%2Fs00001%2F1594186659457%2F%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E6%BC%A2%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E6%8F%AE%E6%8B%B3%E5%82%B7%E4%BA%BA-%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A3%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E7%B7%A9%E5%88%912%E5%B9%B4&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=e3aa86f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200708%2Fs00001%2F1594186659457%2F%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E6%BC%A2%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E6%8F%AE%E6%8B%B3%E5%82%B7%E4%BA%BA-%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A3%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E7%B7%A9%E5%88%912%E5%B9%B4&h=0ad33a18\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200708/s00001/1594186659457/退休漢機場揮拳傷人-判囚3個月緩刑2年</a><br />\n<br />\n大批示威者去年8月9日圍堵香港國際機場，一名抵港男子感不滿，並上前質問舉牌示威者「Free乜嘢Hong Kong？」，又質問機管局職員為何容許示威。該男子隨即被過百名示威者包圍，當中一名退休漢向他揮拳被捕。退休漢今（8日）在西九龍裁判法院承認普通襲擊罪，裁判官認為事件源於被告與事主「對事件有不同睇法」，雖被告「乘人不備」從後施襲，但案件暴力程度不高，事主傷勢不重，判他入獄3個月，緩刑2年。<br />\n<br />\n被告何兆麟（64歲）報稱已退休，辯方求情稱他年事已高，為獨居老人，希望法庭念及他有悔意而輕判。<br />\n<br />\n案情指出，持香港身分證的梁海峯（51歲）去年8月9日傍晚乘客機抵港，入境到達機場客運大樓時見到大量示威者聚集，遂用手機拍攝。梁海峯前往機場的士站，見到一名女子舉「Free Hong Kong」紙牌，他遂上前問女子「Free乜嘢Hong Kong？」，隨即遭在場其他示威者指罵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁海峯之後折返客運大樓，詢問機管局職員為何容許示威者聚集，又稱示威者對其行程造成滋擾。他隨即遭逾百名示威者包圍，並突然感到有人從後揮拳打他的臉，轉身看見被告正後退，他最終在機管局職員護送下離去，驗傷結果稱他鼻樑輕微擦傷。警方其後拘捕被告，梁海峯在認人手續中認出被告。"},{"pid":"1d949a712336c05808f7fc4e139b5a210bc3bf10","tid":2102251,"uid":111070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:38:36.000Z","msg":"閱讀理解拎F?"},{"pid":"c96f136e3e1e4dd54559ab4001acdcc955e79936","tid":2102251,"uid":32244,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:38:55.000Z","msg":"睇清楚內文啦，你係有心定係點？"},{"pid":"57c7a39bf9ceb22e60866e808a8668e481fef036","tid":2102251,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:39:47.000Z","msg":"呢個唔係藍絲,佢係打果位抵港不滿集會人士"},{"pid":"a5ede172121209ff3da5e33d1a6229619e1f98ba","tid":2102251,"uid":180168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:39:58.000Z","msg":"閱讀理解0分?<br />\n擺明係畀人打嗰個先係藍絲"},{"pid":"ab787723bfc89f487f1b2eeda465167755eb1a5d","tid":2102251,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:40:24.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"58df83da5e466a191ff6277763c024fd60e64725","tid":2102251,"uid":2247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:40:37.000Z","msg":"重覆睇左兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以為我get錯 點知原來樓主on9"},{"pid":"7892ad48cd788a49eddcf7880ef140b38065dbc2","tid":2102251,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c96f136e3e1e4dd54559ab4001acdcc955e79936","tid":2102251,"uid":32244,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:38:55.000Z","msg":"睇清楚內文啦，你係有心定係點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:41:28.000Z","msg":"帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12096ab54aafdad3a31034b9feb24e92bd95c418","tid":2102251,"uid":138593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"on9樓主閱讀障礙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041fc93f461c31fc1322e7ee2d50390367e261d8","tid":2102251,"uid":285514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3